        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2840451581" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6255714523181112250"><strong>Building a relationship</strong><br/><br/>I enjoyed the way this book flowed. Tara was a lost soul and worked so hard to thank the people that had helped her along the way. Justin showed up in town and cracked her hard exterior. She also helped him realize how much people work together and are loyal to each other. A great book about how a town goes to great measures to protect the ones they love. This is my first time reading Kirsten Fullmer. I know it will not be my last!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


