ring. With her quirky and protective hometown behind her, will Tara confront Justin and the townâ€™s long buried secrets to take on the financial and emotional risk of a lifetime?â€™<br /><br />Interesting on several levels â€“ historic preservation, traditional approaches vs. entrepreneurial versions of restoration, small town vs. big town attitudes â€“ and Kirsten adds erotica to what seems to be an unlikely compatibility of roles: the result is a fine romance with ample erotica. In Kirsten Fullmerâ€™s hands this novel comes alive with vigor - a refreshing and satisfying experience. Recommended. </span>
